# IPP Whitepaper Series

This directory hosts formal papers, preprints, and extended theoretical documents related to the Informational Projection Paradox (IPP).

## Planned Documents
- **ipp_whitepaper_v1.0.md** — Formal specification of the paradox.
- **ipp_collapse_dynamics.md** — Extended mathematical treatment of entropy growth in X⊥.
- **ipp_civos_integration.md** — Integration of IPP with the Civilization OS framework.

All documents begin as stubs and will be expanded into full academic-style papers.
